snippet.title: Shuffle Tactics - Official Trailer | The Mix Showcase March 2023
snippet.description: Here's your look at Shuffle Tactics, an upcoming game that is a mesh of deck-building and tactical RPGs. Check out the trailer to see combat, some of the battlefields, and more.
